title: Interview: Doug Ryder of Q36.5 Pro Cycling Talks Disparity in Cycling Teams
content:
Doug Ryder has run a host of teams with a scrappy, underdog feel to them, accepting the challenge of competing against the big dogs.

Read the full article at Interview: Doug Ryder of Q36.5 Pro Cycling Talks Disparity in Cycling Teams on Velo.
